Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:06.23,Chiha-note,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Ms. Miyauchi, \NWe have 5 Karuta Club Members!!\NPresident 1-2 Ayase Chihaya\NVice President 1-1 Mashima Taichi\NSecretary 1-2 Komachi Tsutomu\NEquipment Manager 1-8 Nishida Yusei\NTreasurer 1-6 Oe Kanade\N Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:06.23,Chiha-note,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Introductions\N\N\NI'm going to become a Queen!\NClass B jack of all trades.\NA very smart rookie.\NThe roundest player in Class B.\NA very reliable fan of\Nclassical poetry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.63,0:00:07.20,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,You have five members, so you want me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.20,0:00:11.43,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,to officially sanction the Karuta Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.43,0:00:13.49,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.89,0:00:16.74,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.21,0:00:26.18,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.18,0:00:27.15,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.42,0:00:32.62,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,However, change the president \Nto someone other than Ayase-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.62,0:00:33.55,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.55,0:00:35.93,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,I'll serve as the advisor for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.93,0:00:37.64,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.50,0:00:42.15,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't I be the club president?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:44.69,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I think she made a wise decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:47.23,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, \Nwho {\i1}should{\i0} be the club president?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.23,0:00:49.27,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Let Mashima do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.27,0:00:50.85,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.85,0:00:52.38,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,That makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.38,0:00:53.71,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.07,0:00:55.78,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Then that makes Chihaya...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.78,0:00:58.20,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I'll be the captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.64,0:01:01.14,Chiha-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.41,0:01:07.71,Chiha-title,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1700,0)}Chihaya Furu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.15,0:02:15.44,Chiha-note,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(700,0)}Treasurer Notes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.21,0:02:15.44,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Our budget is 3,000 yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.44,0:02:18.21,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,There won't be anything \Nleft after we buy cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.52,0:02:26.00,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Any suggestions about \Nhow we should practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.48,0:02:30.64,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Mashima and I can take \Nturns playing with Ayase.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.64,0:02:32.10,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,The person who isn't playing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.10,0:02:34.11,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,can teach Kana-chan and Desktomu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.11,0:02:35.96,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Tsutomu, Porky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:38.78,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Desktomu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.78,0:02:39.60,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Porky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.60,0:02:40.37,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Desktomu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.37,0:02:40.91,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Porky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.91,0:02:42.06,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,That should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.71,0:02:46.07,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya is Class A,\N so she'll be on a different regimen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.44,0:02:50.35,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Um, is Class A really so special?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.35,0:02:51.51,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,It certainly is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.02,0:02:54.05,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Players start in Class E.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.05,0:02:56.36,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,You have to win tournaments \Nand work your way up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.06,0:02:59.05,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Nishida and I are Class B.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.66,0:03:02.51,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,It depends on which society you belong to,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.51,0:03:05.22,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,but to reach Class A,\N you need to place
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.22,0:03:07.37,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,first or second in two tournaments.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:09.58,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.01,0:03:10.87,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.38,0:03:14.04,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Today, I get Kana-chan and Desktomu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:19.54,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,You want to play against Komano and Oe-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.54,0:03:20.35,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.35,0:03:21.94,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Are you crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.94,0:03:25.46,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Beginners aren't going to learn anything \Nby playing someone in class A!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.46,0:03:26.26,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,But we're gonna play!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.26,0:03:26.67,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.67,0:03:28.68,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be any fun for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:29.51,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,But we're gonna play!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.51,0:03:30.62,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.59,0:03:34.31,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Does the president or the \Ncaptain have more say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.64,0:03:37.19,Chiha-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, good question...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.27,0:03:43.24,Chiha-ep-title-verse,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(900,800)}Verse 9
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.27,0:03:43.24,Chiha-ep-title-poem,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(900,800)}But I\N Cannot\N Hide
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.58,0:03:45.33,Chiha-poem,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes spring, \Nnow the flower blooms
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.78,0:03:56.04,Chiha-poem,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes spring, \Nnow the flower blooms
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.24,0:03:59.21,Chiha-poem,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,While some dodge the famous waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.90,0:04:02.66,Chiha-poem,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Like the sound of...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.66,0:04:03.38,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,She's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:05.76,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, she's not gonna go easy on her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:12.11,Chiha-poem,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,the thistle and brush are \Nblown by the autumn wind
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:14.79,Chiha-poem,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,All alone, I step...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:29.29,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya-chan, this won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.29,0:04:31.45,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,The gap between us is too big.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.03,0:04:35.21,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Kana-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.86,0:04:39.19,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,When I played karuta for \Nthe very first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.19,0:04:41.84,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,my opponent was someone who \Nwas incredibly strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:45.22,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,If he had gone easy on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:49.31,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't love karuta the way I do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.04,0:04:53.10,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,So, I'm not going to go easy on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.54,0:04:54.81,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to try my hardest,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.72,0:04:57.60,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,because I need you guys to become stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.64,0:05:00.42,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,This summer,\N the five of us will
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:03.07,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,participate as a team in \Nthe national tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.67,0:05:11.69,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Omi Jingu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.69,0:05:13.93,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.67,0:05:17.94,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Every July, there's a tournament \Nat the Omi Jingu shrine
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.94,0:05:19.88,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,in the Shiga Prefecture
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.88,0:05:22.72,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,to determine the best high \Nschool karuta players in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.72,0:05:25.13,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,It's considered the Koshien of karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.13,0:05:27.45,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,First, we need to win the Tokyo regionals!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.45,0:05:29.22,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,After that, we'll be in \Nthe national tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.44,0:05:32.91,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Win... National tournament...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.28,0:05:38.24,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Um, how many schools will be \Nparticipating in the Tokyo regionals?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.24,0:05:39.60,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,A whole bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.60,0:05:41.52,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Tokyo is a competitive region!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:46.64,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,W-We can't make nationals.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.64,0:05:48.49,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,We just started playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:49.70,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.15,0:05:51.81,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to play real matches
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.81,0:05:54.26,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,against Desktomu-kun and Kana-chan every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.26,0:05:55.62,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,You better get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.53,0:06:02.54,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure about this, Chihaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.91,0:06:04.52,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.52,0:06:06.29,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,The tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.75,0:06:09.03,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,If you're playing Komano \Nand Oe-san every day,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.03,0:06:10.93,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,you won't have any time \Nfor serious practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:12.51,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:14.10,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine in that department.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.43,0:06:16.53,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,How will you be fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.94,0:06:19.04,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to win the \Nindividual tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.04,0:06:19.99,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.35,0:06:21.94,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.94,0:06:24.07,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,You should be practicing \Nat the Shiranami Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.39,0:06:26.99,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Nishida and I will take \Ncare of the two rookies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.99,0:06:31.01,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.01,0:06:32.01,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.54,0:06:36.95,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember when\N the two of us and Arata
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.89,0:06:40.79,shirt,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Team Chihaya Furu
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.49,0:06:46.00,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,played in a team match for the first time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.23,0:06:50.80,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.11,0:06:58.10,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Positioning is key.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:06:59.06,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Positioning?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.06,0:07:03.75,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, when you're placing the \Ncards on your side of the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.75,0:07:05.42,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible to memorize the position
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:07.65,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,of every card perfectly every match, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.67,0:07:10.38,Chiha-card-TS,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,If my name were sullied \Nby such a brief tryst
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:10.40,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,I already came up with a \Nmethod for placing cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.63,0:07:14.67,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put my favorite cards \Nto the lower right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.67,0:07:18.00,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,But, while putting the "So spring ends" and
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:21.61,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,"So spring nights" cards together \Nmakes it easier for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.61,0:07:23.12,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,you're also making it \Neasier for your opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.07,0:07:26.87,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm not saying that this is a bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.87,0:07:29.42,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine if you have faster \Nreflexes than your opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.16,0:07:34.55,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,The idea is to keep practicing \Nuntil you've learned
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:39.12,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the positions that are easiest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.12,0:07:40.81,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,The most important thing is experience!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.81,0:07:42.02,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play a match!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:42.69,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.69,0:07:43.55,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.98,0:07:47.66,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,I'm left-handed, so I should place \Nmy favorite cards to my left?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.66,0:07:49.80,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that too simple?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.23,0:07:52.53,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Are there any theories about how \Nto position the long shot cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.84,0:07:54.97,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,There are sixteen cards \Nwhich begin with "The"...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.97,0:07:58.41,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Please teach me more\Nabout how to place my cards well!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.92,0:08:01.21,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to lose to \Nsomeone who joined after me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.48,0:08:10.68,Chiha-poem,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,be as dear now, \Nthose were the good old days
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.67,0:08:14.13,Chiha-poem,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,So the flower petals are...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.87,0:08:17.14,Chiha-poem,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Since the dew atop...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:19.77,Chiha-poem,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,After many, many years...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.47,0:08:22.60,Chiha-poem,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,My own home is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.35,0:08:26.94,Chiha-poem,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,I hear the beating of cloth...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.74,0:08:29.74,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? A dead card?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.74,0:08:30.82,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.34,0:08:33.44,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.44,0:08:35.70,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Failure is part of the experience!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.10,0:08:39.12,Chiha-poem,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,While it brings me no joy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:45.33,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,I-I took a card...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.77,0:08:48.98,Chiha-card-TS,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,and I have yet to visit Amanohashidate \Nor read my mother's letters
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.70,0:08:49.00,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,My first card.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:50.00,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,That was great, Kana-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:50.88,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Nice job!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.49,0:08:53.35,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.35,0:08:57.40,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,I promised myself that\NI would take this card today!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.06,0:09:00.43,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.35,0:09:06.12,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Arata, I have people to play with now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.39,0:09:08.86,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.23,0:09:13.52,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm helping to pass on \Nwhat you passed to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.31,0:09:21.76,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,The school is already closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.76,0:09:23.41,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Go home already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.10,0:09:27.22,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Man, we don't have enough time to practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.22,0:09:30.37,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,There's only enough time for \Ntwo matches after classes end?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.37,0:09:32.40,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,I need more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.40,0:09:34.98,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to \Nbuild up any stamina, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.98,0:09:38.43,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,In tournaments, you sometimes have \Nto play at least four matches in one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.03,0:09:40.81,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,The Shiranami Society\N held a two-day camp
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:44.00,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,at Lake Kawaguchi over the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.00,0:09:46.94,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,That was to help us build stamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.68,0:09:49.69,Chiha-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Camp?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:52.65,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, a camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:54.40,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,I like the sound of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.40,0:09:55.65,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hold one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:09:58.12,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,We have a long weekend coming \Nup because of Founder's Day!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.12,0:09:59.03,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.34,0:10:00.64,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,But where do we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.92,0:10:06.09,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,We need a place where we can stay \Novernight and play karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.09,0:10:08.28,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,There are only three weeks until the tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.28,0:10:09.86,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,It makes more sense to just practice
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.86,0:10:12.82,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,instead of wasting time looking \Nfor a good place for a camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.82,0:10:16.92,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,We can try to use lunch and nights \Nto make up the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.25,0:10:18.70,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:22.43,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't think of a place nearby where \Neverybody could stay overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.97,0:10:25.98,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.49,0:10:27.27,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:34.86,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,It was a stroke of luck that Taichi's \Nparents are in Kobe for a wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.84,0:10:40.10,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,With Founder's Day,\N we can play karuta all weekend!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.92,0:10:43.62,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,There's an empty room and extra futons,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.62,0:10:45.58,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,but are you seriously going \Nto spend the night here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.36,0:10:48.71,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. I'm the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.63,0:10:52.85,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.85,0:10:55.50,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Show me your room\N before everyone gets here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.50,0:10:56.25,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.65,0:10:59.27,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,We used to play games there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.27,0:11:02.51,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a new big TV or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.87,0:11:04.48,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.84,0:11:06.93,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Now look here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.72,0:11:13.73,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be running \Nto a guy's room like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:15.76,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna let you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.23,0:11:38.51,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Mashima...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.99,0:11:43.58,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,For the first time in my life,\N I feel like we live in a class society.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:45.37,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.37,0:11:47.89,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, did you buy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.73,0:11:49.68,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,You bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.48,0:11:54.43,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really excited about this camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.43,0:11:55.97,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,What are we having for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.97,0:11:57.23,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,How about a test of courage?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.23,0:11:58.40,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,I like the sound of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.40,0:11:59.82,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a graveyard nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.41,0:12:04.38,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,These are all Mashima's?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.38,0:12:05.30,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.83,0:12:10.99,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Eiken Grade Pre-1, violin, \Nhorse riding, skiing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.99,0:12:12.08,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.32,0:12:15.34,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my parents made me \Ntake all kinds of lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.45,0:12:19.71,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Man, why did Chihaya have \Nto show them those?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.05,0:12:22.42,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is this your mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.67,0:12:24.73,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,She's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.73,0:12:29.34,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh, but I don't really \Nlike Taichi's mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.34,0:12:30.00,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.39,0:12:32.31,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,She gets mad when he doesn't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.80,0:12:35.44,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I called her "Mrs. Pressure."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.59,0:12:41.02,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you here to practice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.23,0:12:45.00,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I have an announcement to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.00,0:12:49.41,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,The goal of the first Mizusawa High \NSchool Karuta Club camp is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.03,0:12:52.91,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,to play 15 matches today and tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.36,0:12:55.67,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,F-Fifteen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.69,0:13:00.34,Chiha-note2,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Match Schedule (Day One)\NReader: Taichi      Desktomu-kun vs Kana-chan     Chihaya vs Porky\NReader: Porky     Desktomu-kun vs Chihaya     Taichi vs Kana-chan\NReader: Chihaya     Desktomu-kun vs Taichi     Porky vs Kana-chan\NReader: Taichi     Desktomu-kun vs Porky     Kana-chan vs Chihaya\NReader: Porky     Chihaya vs Taichi     Desktomu-kun vs Kana-chan\NReader: Chihaya     Desktomu-kun vs Porky     Kana-chan vs Taichi {GODDAMN SIGNS -tly}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.97,0:12:57.89,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I made a schedule!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.33,0:13:00.34,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Ch-Chihaya-chan, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:03.30,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Desktomu-kun and I don't get any breaks...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.30,0:13:07.42,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. The most important thing \Nright now is to play matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.42,0:13:08.79,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Stay focused in every match!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.93,0:13:13.60,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Kana-chan, your swing is too big!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:17.48,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't using the form I taught you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:19.73,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Desktomu-kun, you should use \Na thrust for that card!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:21.73,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Stay focused!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.76,0:13:25.25,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to become better!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.85,0:13:28.32,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I want to help you win!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.35,0:13:31.86,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.77,0:13:38.63,Chiha-note2,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,750)}Match Schedule (Day One)\NReader: Taichi      Desktomu-kun vs Kana-chan     Chihaya vs Porky\NReader: Porky     Desktomu-kun vs Chihaya     Taichi vs Kana-chan\NReader: Chihaya     Desktomu-kun vs Taichi     Porky vs Kana-chan\NReader: Taichi     Desktomu-kun vs Porky     Kana-chan vs Chihaya\NReader: Porky     Chihaya vs Taichi     Desktomu-kun vs Kana-chan\NReader: Chihaya     Desktomu-kun vs Porky     Kana-chan vs Taichi
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.92,0:13:35.95,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For now, we have to practice!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.75,0:13:46.91,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Um, next is Desktomu-kun vs \NPorky and Kana-chan vs...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.91,0:13:47.63,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:48.14,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.52,0:13:49.90,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Let's call it a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.90,0:13:52.98,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Why? We've only played five matches!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.50,0:13:54.33,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.03,0:14:03.80,Chiha-poem,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,May I live to see the day when
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.35,0:14:11.22,Chiha-poem,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,I long for the agony I feel now
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.22,0:14:12.91,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,They're both spent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.19,0:14:17.09,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,But it'll be just as hard in a tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.09,0:14:18.32,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we have to keep practicing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.32,0:14:19.45,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.88,0:14:22.29,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to break people \Nwho are trying their best?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:27.74,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.28,0:14:37.09,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,That hit the spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.09,0:14:39.90,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad that Mashima is the president!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.28,0:14:47.62,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You guys aren't eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.55,0:14:50.23,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,I have no appetite.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.58,0:14:52.13,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:56.16,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Although, we have to eat \Nsomething or we won't last!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.65,0:14:58.66,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Desktomu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:01.00,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our best to eat something!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.42,0:15:03.42,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,We have to practice more tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.05,0:15:05.42,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Desktomu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.15,0:15:09.30,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Kana-chan, we have to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:10.18,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:11.85,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Just hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.23,0:15:18.81,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,M-M—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:20.61,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.61,0:15:23.44,Chiha-main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Taichi. You're having friends over?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.99,0:15:26.70,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were staying overnight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.70,0:15:29.87,Chiha-main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Rika suddenly said that \Nshe wanted to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.87,0:15:33.00,Chiha-main,Rika,0000,0000,0000,,No point in me staying if \Nwe weren't going to USJ!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.47,0:15:35.76,Chiha-main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Rika is so fickle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.51,0:15:36.70,Chiha-overlap,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Whew, that was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:39.43,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's grab our shoes and go to my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.43,0:15:42.54,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Mrs. Pressure would never \Nlet girls stay overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.62,0:15:46.59,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Kana-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.49,0:16:10.46,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to break people \Nwho are trying their best?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.90,0:16:18.20,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it, \Npeople always used to tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.59,0:16:22.61,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,that I was blind to \Neverything but karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.35,0:16:29.51,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.19,0:16:32.57,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,No good at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:36.49,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.91,0:16:40.10,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.08,0:16:43.86,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me, Chihaya-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.86,0:16:44.61,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.61,0:16:45.73,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.32,0:16:48.45,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, Kana-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.63,0:16:53.18,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Kana-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.84,0:16:55.70,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we going in the \Nmiddle of the night?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.82,0:17:00.39,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kana-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.36,0:17:03.02,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, how far are we going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.37,0:17:04.37,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.46,0:17:08.13,Chiha-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.25,0:17:11.63,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi? And everyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.82,0:17:17.72,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about calling you out here so late,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.19,0:17:22.85,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,but we had something to tell you, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:26.93,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Let me go first!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.35,0:17:28.86,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about today!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.86,0:17:30.03,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.31,0:17:34.42,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I needed to pay more attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:38.87,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone was trying their best, \Nbut I kept pushing you too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.43,0:17:40.87,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.29,0:17:48.13,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see any problem \Nwith what you were doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.13,0:17:49.16,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.99,0:17:52.82,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,You just happen to be a pushy person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.82,0:17:55.63,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't hurt to have one of those around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:17:57.57,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Porky...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.57,0:17:58.76,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.37,0:18:05.01,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,We have to work hard because \Nyou're so earnest about karuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.43,0:18:06.58,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Kana-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.09,0:18:08.02,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,I feel the same way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.49,0:18:10.67,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,I still have much to learn,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.17,0:18:13.65,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,but I have a feeling that \NI'll grow to love karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.41,0:18:15.65,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Desktomu-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.41,0:18:19.82,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.68,0:18:26.16,Chiha-Sign-top,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.07,0:18:27.92,Chiha-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:32.76,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Now eat this quick,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.76,0:18:35.34,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,before Mashima's mom finishes her bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:37.96,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! I forgot to bring a knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.96,0:18:39.14,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, these are spoons!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.14,0:18:41.10,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Man, just eat it whole!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.10,0:18:42.52,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,That's bad manners!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.52,0:18:44.02,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.02,0:18:46.35,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Chihaya, here's the nameplate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.35,0:18:47.67,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.67,0:18:49.88,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious! What's this yellow stuff?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.88,0:18:51.23,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,That's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.23,0:18:53.76,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and eat, Chihaya-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.54,0:19:07.78,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya, as long as you \Nhave a smile on your face,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.78,0:19:09.12,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,karuta will always be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.07,0:19:12.46,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,That's the truth, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.09,0:19:21.81,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I really like the tart crust.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.81,0:19:24.34,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Can I peel off the edge?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.34,0:19:25.34,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.34,0:19:26.69,Chiha-main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.69,0:19:29.35,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,It's her birthday, \Nso she can do what she wants!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.80,0:19:32.30,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! I'll help myself then!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.34,0:19:35.86,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,It's so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.17,0:19:39.54,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Mashima's mom is a little scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.54,0:19:42.24,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody should go lock her in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.61,0:19:43.95,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.95,0:19:44.91,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.91,0:19:46.24,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Me either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.08,0:19:54.96,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,From an unknown number?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.40,0:20:08.67,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.16,0:20:13.27,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you the last bit of crust!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.76,0:20:15.90,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding! It's all mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.34,0:20:26.37,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, Mashima's mom really scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.64,0:20:40.51,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,There was a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.51,0:20:41.26,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.26,0:20:42.01,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.70,0:20:47.26,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a shooting star!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.26,0:20:48.20,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.55,0:20:49.52,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.52,0:20:51.57,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen one before!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.02,0:21:01.32,cellphone,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\\fad(0,600)}Taichi, sorry about before. \NTell Chihaya happy birthday for me.\NWataya Arata
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.46,0:20:59.98,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet sixteen...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.24,0:21:08.03,cellphone2,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\\fad(600,0)}Wataya Arata
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.96,0:21:16.08,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Today is the best birthday ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.15,0:21:18.44,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, look! Another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.44,0:21:19.30,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.30,0:21:21.19,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.19,0:21:22.99,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it was so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.99,0:21:25.34,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,I missed it again!
